 "2007 Dispositions:", "bbox": [137.6, 1198.2, 295.6, 1219.1]}, {"text": "On November 7, 2007, the Company sold ADS MB Corporation, which operated its mail services business", "bbox": [179.2, 1231.7, 1072.7, 1252.5]}, {"text": "which was included in its Transaction services segment. The Company received total proceeds of $12.3 million", "bbox": [137.6, 1256.7, 1067.9, 1277.5]}, {"text": "and recognized a pre-tax loss of approximately $16.0 million.", "bbox": [137.6, 1281.7, 652.4, 1302.5]}, {"text": "2006 Acquisitions:", "bbox": [137.6, 1331.4, 294.5, 1352.2]}, {"text": "In February 2006, the Company acquired Toronto-based iCOM Information & Communications, Inc.", "bbox": [179.2, 1364.8, 1025.5, 1385.7]}, {"text": "(“iCOM”), a leading provider of targeted list, marketing data and communications solutions for the", "bbox": [137.6, 1389.8, 966.4, 1410.7]}, {"text": "pharmaceutical, tobacco and fast moving consumer goods industries in North America. Total consideration paid", "bbox": [137.6, 1414.9, 1074.0, 1435.7]}, {"text": "F-16", "bbox": [593.1, 1465.8, 632.4, 1486.6]}]}